{"tid":2147903,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今日我去探手足，手足同我講左一件事","createTime":"2020-08-09T14:20:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T04:18:39.000Z","uid":178726,"like":20,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5aa5230e335a0043e13817cc7b1928505b8ed87b","tid":2147903,"uid":178726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:20:40.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\">是咁的，我今日去咗LCK探手足，<strong><span class=\"red\">手足叫我share出去</span></strong></p><br />\n<br />\n由於得15分鐘時間，所以佢都長話短說啦，就最近有一個手足個名就叫 <strong><span class=\"orange\">羅皓譽</span></strong>(花名: 啊樹，英文名: pepper)，因為上年理大附近藏有武器，判監10個月，大家可以google佢個名睇下。<br />\n<br />\n咁入正題啦，依個人呢，就問社運組織(例:612)同家長周圍claim錢<span class=\"red\"><strong>食人血饅頭</strong></span>，然後就自己去買咗一部車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span class=\"x-large\">仲要同身邊D人<span class=\"orange\">講社運D錢好易呃</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，結果依件事傳翻入去LCK，然後LCK入面嘅各路手足已透過各自嘅探訪人士FC咗依件事，所以手足們要求公諸於世"},{"pid":"f83093b5ad8ab974abad44307f036c9b89abe225","tid":2147903,"uid":288270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5aa5230e335a0043e13817cc7b1928505b8ed87b","tid":2147903,"uid":178726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T14:20:40.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\">是咁的，我今日去咗LCK探手足，<strong><span class=\"red\">手足叫我share出去</span></strong></p><br />\n<br />\n由於得15分鐘時間，所以佢都長話短說啦，就最近有一個手足個名就叫 <strong><span class=\"orange\">羅皓譽</span></strong>(花名: 啊樹，英文名: pepper)，因為上年理大附近藏有武器，判監10個月，大家可以google佢個名睇下。<br />\n<br />\n咁入正題啦，依個人呢，就問社運組織(例:612)同家長周圍claim錢<span class=\"red\"><strong>食人血饅頭</strong></span>，然後就自己去買咗一部車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kil